{"shortcode": "DLHlTFIvM-E", "caption": "Gotta do what you gotta do.
Like and share if you enjoyed it 🥰
Dms are always open

Lyrics : 

Di scene me dastak beat pe kare "knock knock" 
Locked aim hai kaviyo pe kare scene me nok jhok
lacking the passion rapping me, diss hai inka top shauk
toh aana ni tum close mere ganno ke liye hai sauce bohot
gayab inka whole block hai shauk sabha me
Tej hawa se udane mujhe note kamake
Dhoom dhamake kradu beat pe kaun gawah de
bars se bhage idol tera dhuum dabake brr

kitne rapper bikke mere feat ke daam pe
mere feet aaram le 
par defeat ki raatein dekhe
hogya ek baras ab baraste leke verse
jab ghazal pe dabbe shuffle toh samjho trouble hai double
mere level pe yeh pebble aake bane kewal khabar
khojo mera shovel shav banake khodu inki kabar ab
Jaaake kro cover up
kyu chodi itni baatein
raatein jaag ke jhaant ukhada 
baap ki belt pdegi buckle up

Denge dakhal Yeh likhayi degi taklife
Khake scene pura jayu chai pinne tapri pe
Vibe hai deadly aur Gayiki pe shaq ni hai
Dikhtaa hai inn aankho me yeh rap hi ab taqdeer h

Tabhi na koi idol 
Hum bas khud se seekhte
